api_list.name: turnstile getResult
api_list.description: Get the `token` for the Cloudflare Turnstille CAPTCHA solver task
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://turnstile-captcha-solver.p.rapidapi.com/get_result"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "turnstile-captcha-solver.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
